workDescription1: Led the successful implementation of Constructor.io Search, increasing adoption from 10% to 100% and improving search relevancy, performance, and conversion rates. Designed and executed robust solutions, including new operations, endpoints, resolvers, and queries, while implementing fallback strategies for seamless transitions. Developed business logic using technologies like NodeRed, Node.js, and Sequelize, and created UI designs aligned with business requirements using Vue.js, React, Redux, Next.js, and Material UI. Optimized development workflows, integrated A/B tests with Adobe Target, and enhanced system reliability through SumoLogic monitoring. Led agile project implementations, mentored team members, and collaborated with design teams to ensure user-friendly experiences.
workDescription2: Develop complex business logic and data binding using Next.js, React, Redux, Java Spring Boot Microservices, Node.js, AWS, and DynamoDB to enhance performance and functionality. Execute UI designs with React, Redux, Next.js, Nike Design System, and CSS for a seamless user experience. Optimize development, testing, and deployment workflows using React, Node, Jest, SQL Server, Jenkins, and AWS. Manage and enhance web content with Optimizely CMS, driving user engagement and conversion. Implement A/B tests and personalization strategies to improve retention. Provide global support for Login and Registration Modules. Mentor team members, enforce coding best practices, and conduct thorough code reviews. Establish reusable components and development patterns for high-quality, scalable code. Collaborate with cross-functional teams using Jira and agile methodologies for efficient project execution. Leverage AWS services to optimize functionalities. Align product implementations with intuitive, user-friendly designs. Lead in agile environments, ensuring timely project deliveries and effective team operations.
